COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: COUNTYWIDE; CALIFORNIA SAVINGS BONDS OFFERED FOR SALE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Investors can purchase California Savings Bonds during an eight-day ordering 
period that begins today. 
</P>
<P>
 State Treasury officials said the savings bonds are attractive to small 
investors because they come in $1,000 denominations. 
</P>
<P>
 Bond income is free of federal and state taxes. Officials said the bonds are 
often used by families saving money for college. 
</P>
<P>
 For more information, call (800) 203-3151. 
</P>
