COMMUNITY NEWS FOCUS: NEWPORT BEACH; ENTRIES ARE SOLICITED FOR ANNUAL ART SHOW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By HOLLY J. WAGNER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city's Arts Commission is seeking entries for its annual fall art show, to 
be held in November. 
</P>
<P>
 Local artists may submit up to three works for a $5 entry fee. The deadline 
for entries is Oct.26. Prizes will be awarded for top selections, and some 
artwork will be displayed at City Hall. 
</P>
<P>
 For an entry form or more information, call the commission at (714) 644-3150. 
HOLLY J. WAGNER 
