<P>
 "Five interceptions. Geez, that's tough. Three's the most I've ever thrown in 
a game, and that was when I was 11."  
</P>
<P>
 -- Redskin quarterback Heath Shuler, on his performance in the 19-16 overtime 
loss to Arizona: 
</P>
