Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA101794-0051 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 089406 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 17, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part C; Page 15; Column 2; Sports Desk 
</P>
