<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEILE ADAMS TO DEBUT HER CABARET SHOW 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Neile Adams will debut her cabaret show at the Hollywood Roosevelt's Cinegrill 
with performances Friday and Oct. 24 at 8:30 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Her show, in which she makes the transition from dancer to singer, traces her 
career from Broadway soubrette to Hollywood wife and mother -- she was married 
to the late actor Steve McQueen for 15 years -- to her new performing career. 
</P>
<P>
 Reservations and information: (213) 466-7000. 
</P>
</TEXT>
