passenger in a car at Yucca Street and Wilcox Avenue in Hollywood about 1 a.m. 
when he and a group of gang members approached the vehicle and "exchanged 
words" with the occupants, according to a Los Angeles Police Department 
statement. 
</P>
<P>
 The car drove off and the transient died at a nearby hospital 30 minutes 
later. 
</P>
