(exhibition). What else can happen? I've had all the bad . . . happen to me. 
What else can happen?" 
</P>
<P>
 Another start, perhaps? Slater is expected to be sidelined through the bye 
week, meaning Gandy will be protecting quarterback Chris Miller again Sunday in 
New Orleans. 
</P>
<P>
