defensive player (Hamilton). He should be awfully proud of himself." 
</P>
<P>
 Belin got his first NFL start, taking over at left guard. 
</P>
<P>
 "It feels good to get a victory after you've been working so hard all week," 
Belin said. "There was much more stress this week than a typical week." 
</P>
<P>
 Miller praised the play of Belin and Gandy. 
</P>
<P>
 "They did a great job," he said. "We had a couple of sacks in the second half, 
but that was mostly because of a scheme we weren't prepared for. I had a lot of 
time to step up and find my guys and throw. It's nice to have guys who can step 
in and get the job done." 
</P>
<P>
 Farr was waiting for such an opportunity. He wasn't drafted last spring, 
mainly because he is small for an NFL lineman. But the Rams took a chance on 
him -- and he has made it pay off. 
</P>
